# 📂 Documentation

This directory contains the architecture notes, data models, and platform observations gathered during the 4-week Palantir Foundry sprint.

## 🧱 Core Concepts Logged
* **Foundry Ontology:** Notes on object types, properties, and many-to-many/one-to-many link definitions.
* **Data Lineage:** Tracing how raw source datasets map to production objects.
* **Security & Markings:** Best practices implemented for column-level and dataset-level security access.
